         <li>
            <p>Carry the load as low as possible but maintain clearance.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>On grades, always travel with the load on the UPHILL side, as shown above. </p>
            <p>
               <p>
                  <fig id="fig_asm_kyy_5gc">
                     <image href="media/image792.png" id="image_csm_kyy_5gc" placement="inline"/>
